#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:3
msgid "Conversations"
msgstr "Comhráite"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:5
msgid ""
"Chats and calls take place in conversations. You can create any number of "
"conversations. There are different types of conversations:"
msgstr ""
"Bíonn comhráite agus glaonna ar siúl i gcomhráite. Is féidir leat aon líon "
"comhráite a chruthú. Tá cineálacha éagsúla comhráite ann:"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:8
msgid "1. Private (one-to-one) conversations"
msgstr "1. Comhráite príobháideacha (duine le duine)"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:9
msgid "This is where you have a private chat or call with another Talk user."
msgstr ""
"Seo an áit a mbíonn comhrá príobháideach nó glao gutháin agat le húsáideoir "
"Talk eile."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:11
msgid ""
"In the content sidebar, you can find additional information about the person"
" you are chatting with, such as their email address, phone number, or other "
"details they have shared in their profile."
msgstr ""
"Sa bharra taoibh ábhair, is féidir leat faisnéis bhreise a fháil faoin duine"
" a bhfuil tú ag comhrá leis, amhail a seoladh ríomhphoist, a n-uimhir "
"theileafóin, nó sonraí eile atá roinnte acu ina bpróifíl."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:16
msgid ""
"Nobody except you and the other person can see this conversation or join a "
"call in it. You can extend an ongoing call to a new group conversation by "
"adding more people. Call will be continued there without interruption."
msgstr ""
"Ní féidir le haon duine ach tusa agus an duine eile an comhrá seo a "
"fheiceáil ná páirt a ghlacadh i nglao ann. Is féidir leat glao atá ar siúl a"
" shíneadh chuig comhrá grúpa nua trí níos mó daoine a chur leis. Leanfar "
"leis an nglao ansin gan cur isteach."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:22
msgid ""
"If a user becomes unavailable and has set an **out-of-office** status in "
"``Personal settings > Availability``, you will find additional information "
"in this conversation, such as provided description, absence date, or their "
"replacement person."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil úsáideoir ar fáil agus má shocraigh sé stádas **as an oifig** i "
"``Socruithe Pearsanta > Infhaighteacht``, gheobhaidh tú faisnéis bhreise sa "
"chomhrá seo, amhail an cur síos a tugadh, dáta na neamhláithreachta, nó a "
"n-ionadaí."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:28
msgid "2. Group conversations"
msgstr "2. Comhráite grúpa"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:29
msgid ""
"A group conversation can have any number of people in it. You can add "
"internal users, email guests, groups or teams to a group conversation upon "
"creation, or when it already exists, via the ``Participants`` tab."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir aon líon daoine a bheith i gcomhrá grúpa. Is féidir leat "
"úsáideoirí inmheánacha, ríomhphoist a sheoladh chuig aíonna, grúpaí nó "
"foirne a chur le comhrá grúpa nuair a chruthaítear é, nó nuair a bhíonn sé "
"ann cheana féin, tríd an táb ``Rannpháirtithe``."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:32
msgid ""
"A group conversation can be shared with a public link, so guests can join a "
"chat and a call. It can also be opened to registered users (or users from "
"'Guests' app), so they can discover and join this conversation."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir comhrá grúpa a roinnt le nasc poiblí, ionas gur féidir le haíonna "
"páirt a ghlacadh i gcomhrá agus i nglao. Is féidir é a oscailt d'úsáideoirí "
"cláraithe (nó d'úsáideoirí ón aip 'Aíonna') freisin, ionas gur féidir leo an"
" comhrá seo a aimsiú agus páirt a ghlacadh ann."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:40
msgid "3. Note to self"
msgstr "3. Nóta dom féin"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:41
msgid ""
"This is a special conversation with yourself. Messages here do not have a "
"limit for editing or deletion. You can use it to:"
msgstr ""
"Is comhrá speisialta leat féin é seo. Níl aon teorainn le heagarthóireacht "
"ná le scriosadh teachtaireachtaí anseo. Is féidir leat é a úsáid chun:"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:43
msgid ""
"**Take notes**: write down ideas, reminders, or important information you "
"want to keep handy."
msgstr ""
"**Glac nótaí**: scríobh síos smaointe, meabhrúcháin, nó faisnéis "
"thábhachtach ar mhaith leat a choinneáil ar láimh."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:44
msgid ""
"**Create to-do lists**: use Markdown syntax to create checklists for tasks "
"you need to complete."
msgstr ""
"**Cruthaigh liostaí le déanamh**: bain úsáid as comhréir Markdown chun "
"seicliostaí a chruthú le haghaidh tascanna a chaithfidh tú a chur i gcrích."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:45
msgid ""
"**Forward messages from other chat**: use the message menu to forward "
"important messages from other conversations to your Note to self."
msgstr ""
"**Teachtaireachtaí ar aghaidh ó chomhráite eile**: bain úsáid as an "
"roghchlár teachtaireachtaí chun teachtaireachtaí tábhachtacha ó chomhráite "
"eile a chur ar aghaidh chuig do Nóta duit féin."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:51
msgid "4. Disposable conversations"
msgstr "4. Comhráite indiúscartha"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:52
msgid ""
"These conversations cover some special cases and exist for a limited period "
"of time. Retention period can be configured by an instance administration:"
msgstr ""
"Clúdaíonn na comhráite seo roinnt cásanna speisialta agus bíonn siad ann ar "
"feadh tréimhse teoranta ama. Is féidir le riarachán sampla an tréimhse "
"choinneála a chumrú:"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Instant meetings**: these conversations can be created for quick, ad-hoc "
"meetings. They can be started instantly from the Talk Dashboard."
msgstr ""
"**Cruinnithe meandracha**: is féidir na comhráite seo a chruthú le haghaidh "
"cruinnithe tapa, ad hoc. Is féidir iad a thosú láithreach ón Painéal Comhrá."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:55
msgid ""
"**Event conversations**: these are created when set as an event location by "
"Calendar app."
msgstr ""
"**Comhráite imeachta**: cruthaítear iad seo nuair a shocraítear iad mar "
"shuíomh imeachta ag an aip Féilire."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:56
msgid ""
"**Phone conversations**: these are dedicated for SIP dial-in & dial-out "
"phone calls (requires a SIP gateway)."
msgstr ""
"**Comhráite gutháin**: tá siad seo tiomnaithe do ghlaonna gutháin SIP "
"isteach agus amach (éilíonn sé geata SIP)."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:57
msgid ""
"**Video verification**: these are created, when someone tries to access a "
"public link, protected by password with video verification (deleted "
"instantly after call ends)."
msgstr ""
"**Fíorú físe**: cruthaítear iad seo nuair a dhéanann duine iarracht rochtain"
" a fháil ar nasc poiblí, atá cosanta ag pasfhocal le fíorú físe (scriostar "
"láithreach tar éis dheireadh an ghlao)."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:63
msgid "Talk Dashboard"
msgstr "Painéal Comhrá"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:65
msgid ""
"The Talk Dashboard is your central hub for managing and accessing your "
"conversations. It provides an overview of your:"
msgstr ""
"Is é Painéal na Comhrá an mol lárnach atá agat chun do chomhráite a "
"bhainistiú agus rochtain a fháil orthu. Tugann sé forbhreathnú ar do chuid:"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:67
msgid "Unread mentions and messages in private chats;"
msgstr "Luaitear agus teachtaireachtaí gan léamh i gcomhráite príobháideacha;"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:68
msgid "Message reminders, scheduled to be tackled on later;"
msgstr ""
"Meabhrúcháin teachtaireachtaí, sceidealaithe le dul i ngleic leo níos "
"déanaí;"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:69
msgid ""
"Scheduled meetings, with event details and shortcut buttons to join them;"
msgstr ""
"Cruinnithe sceidealaithe, le sonraí imeachta agus cnaipí aicearra chun páirt"
" a ghlacadh iontu;"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:70
msgid ""
"Shortcut actions to create new conversations, join open ones, or quickly "
"check your media devices."
msgstr ""
"Gníomhartha gearrthéarmacha chun comhráite nua a chruthú, páirt a ghlacadh i"
" gcomhráite oscailte, nó do ghléasanna meán a sheiceáil go tapa."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:76
msgid "Creating a conversation"
msgstr "Comhrá á chruthú"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:78
msgid ""
"You can create a private (one-to-one) chat by searching for the name of a "
"user, a group or a team and clicking it. For a single user, a conversation "
"is immediately created and you can start your chat. For a group or circle "
"you get to pick a name and settings before you create the conversation and "
"add the participants."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat comhrá príobháideach (duine le duine) a chruthú trí ainm "
"úsáideora, grúpa nó foirne a chuardach agus cliceáil air. I gcás úsáideora "
"aonair, cruthaítear comhrá láithreach agus is féidir leat do chomhrá a "
"thosú. I gcás grúpa nó ciorcail, is féidir leat ainm agus socruithe a roghnú"
" sula gcruthaíonn tú an comhrá agus sula gcuireann tú na rannpháirtithe "
"leis."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:83
msgid ""
"If you want to create a custom group conversation, click the button next to "
"the search field and filters button and then on ``Create a new "
"conversation``."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat comhrá grúpa saincheaptha a chruthú, cliceáil an cnaipe in "
"aice leis an réimse cuardaigh agus an cnaipe scagairí agus ansin ar "
"``Cruthaigh comhrá nua``."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:88
msgid ""
"You can then pick a name for the conversation, put a description, and set up"
" an avatar for it (with uploaded photo or emoji), and select if the "
"conversation should be open to external users and if other users on the "
"server can see and join the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Ansin is féidir leat ainm a roghnú don chomhrá, cur síos a chur leis, agus "
"avatar a shocrú dó (le grianghraf uaslódáilte nó emoji), agus a roghnú an "
"bhfuil an comhrá oscailte d’úsáideoirí seachtracha agus an féidir le "
"húsáideoirí eile ar an bhfreastalaí an comhrá a fheiceáil agus páirt a "
"ghlacadh ann."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:93
msgid ""
"In the second step, you get to add participants and finalize the creation of"
" the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Sa dara céim, is féidir leat rannpháirtithe a chur leis agus cruthú an "
"chomhrá a chríochnú."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:98
msgid ""
"After confirmation you will be redirected to the new conversation and can "
"start communicating right away."
msgstr ""
"Tar éis an deimhnithe, atreorófar chuig an gcomhrá nua thú agus is féidir "
"leat tosú ag cumarsáid láithreach."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:104
msgid "Filter your conversations"
msgstr "Scag do chomhráite"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:106
msgid ""
"You can filter your conversations using the filter button next to the search"
" field. There are several options for filtering: 1. **Unread mentions**: "
"view unread private conversations, or group conversations, where you have "
"been mentioned. 2. **Unread messages**: view unread messages in all "
"conversations you are a part of. 3. **Event conversations**: view all "
"conversations, created for upcoming or past events."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do chomhráite a scagadh trí úsáid a bhaint as an gcnaipe "
"scagaire in aice leis an réimse cuardaigh. Tá roinnt roghanna ann le "
"haghaidh scagtha: 1. **Luaitear gan léamh**: féach ar chomhráite "
"príobháideacha gan léamh, nó ar chomhráite grúpa, inar luadh thú. 2. "
"**Teachtaireachtaí gan léamh**: féach ar theachtaireachtaí gan léamh i ngach"
" comhrá ina bhfuil tú páirteach. 3. **Comhráite imeachtaí**: féach ar gach "
"comhrá, a cruthaíodh d’imeachtaí atá le teacht nó san am atá thart."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:114
msgid "You can then clear the filter from the filters menu."
msgstr "Ansin is féidir leat an scagaire a ghlanadh ón roghchlár scagairí."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:120
msgid "Archive conversations"
msgstr "Cartlannaigh comhráite"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:121
msgid ""
"You can archive conversations that you no longer need to see in your main "
"conversation list. When a conversation is archived, it will be moved to the "
"``Archived conversations`` section. An archived conversation will not appear"
" in your main conversation list, but it will still align with notification "
"level set in its settings."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat comhráite nach gá duit a fheiceáil a thuilleadh i do "
"phríomhliosta comhráite a chartlannú. Nuair a dhéantar comhrá a chartlannú, "
"aistreofar é go dtí an rannán ``Comhráite Cartlannaithe``. Ní bheidh comhrá "
"cartlannaithe le feiceáil i do phríomhliosta comhráite, ach beidh sé fós "
"ailínithe leis an leibhéal fógra atá socraithe ina shocruithe."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:127
msgid ""
"The list is accessible from the button at the bottom of the navigation bar."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir rochtain a fháil ar an liosta ón gcnaipe ag bun an bharra "
"nascleanúna."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:133
msgid "Managing a conversation"
msgstr "Comhrá a bhainistiú"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:135
msgid ""
"You are always moderator in your new conversation. In the participant list "
"you can promote other participants to moderators using the ``...`` menu to "
"the right of their user name, assign them custom permissions or remove them "
"from the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Is tusa an modhnóir i gcónaí i do chomhrá nua. Sa liosta rannpháirtithe is "
"féidir leat rannpháirtithe eile a ardú céime go modhnóirí ag baint úsáide as"
" an roghchlár ``...`` ar dheis a n-ainm úsáideora, ceadanna saincheaptha a "
"shannadh dóibh nó iad a bhaint den chomhrá."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:137
msgid ""
"Changing permissions of a user that joined a public conversation will also "
"permanently add them to the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Má athraítear ceadanna úsáideora a chuaigh isteach i gcomhrá poiblí, "
"cuirfear an t-úsáideoir sin leis an gcomhrá go buan freisin."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:142
msgid ""
"Moderators can configure the conversation. Select ``Conversation settings`` "
"from the ``...`` menu of the conversation on the top to access the settings."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le modhnóirí an comhrá a chumrú. Roghnaigh ``Socruithe comhrá`` ón"
" roghchlár ``...`` den chomhrá ag an mbarr chun rochtain a fháil ar na "
"socruithe."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:147
msgid ""
"Here you can configure the description, guest access, if the conversation is"
" visible to others on the server and more."
msgstr ""
"Anseo is féidir leat an cur síos, rochtain aoi, cibé an bhfuil an comhrá le "
"feiceáil ag daoine eile ar an bhfreastalaí agus tuilleadh a chumrú."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:153
msgid "Ban participants"
msgstr "Toirmeasc ar rannpháirtithe"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:155
msgid ""
"To help keep discussions safe and under control, moderators can ban "
"participants from conversations. This applies to internal users and guests "
"alike; for guests, their IP address will also be banned."
msgstr ""
"Chun cabhrú le plé a choinneáil sábháilte agus faoi smacht, is féidir le "
"modhnóirí cosc ​​a chur ar rannpháirtithe ó chomhráite. Baineann sé seo le "
"húsáideoirí inmheánacha agus le haíonna araon; i gcás aíonna, cuirfear cosc "
"​​​​ar a seoladh IP freisin."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:158
msgid ""
"In the participants list, select the user or guest, and click ``Remove "
"participant``."
msgstr ""
"Sa liosta rannpháirtithe, roghnaigh an t-úsáideoir nó an t-aoi, agus "
"cliceáil ar ``Bain rannpháirtí``."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:163
msgid ""
"There, toggle checkbox ``Also ban from this conversation`` and provide a "
"reason for the ban. The banned user will be removed and prevented from "
"rejoining."
msgstr ""
"Ansin, múch an bosca seiceála ``Toirmeasc ón gcomhrá seo freisin`` agus "
"tabhair cúis leis an toirmeasc. Bainfear an t-úsáideoir toirmiscthe agus "
"cuirfear cosc ​​​​air athpháirt a ghlacadh."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:168
msgid ""
"You can later find the list of banned users in the ``Moderation`` section of"
" conversation settings. Here, you can see the reason for the ban and revert "
"it if needed."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat liosta na n-úsáideoirí toirmiscthe a fháil níos déanaí sa "
"rannán ``Modhnóireacht`` de shocruithe an chomhrá. Anseo, is féidir leat "
"cúis an toirmisc a fheiceáil agus é a aisiompú más gá."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:175
msgid "Messages expiration"
msgstr "Éaga teachtaireachtaí"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:177
msgid ""
"A moderator can configure message expiration under the ``Conversation "
"settings`` within the ``Moderation`` section. Once a message reaches its "
"expiration time, it is automatically removed from the conversation. The "
"available expiration durations are 1 hour, 8 hours, 1 day, 1 week, 4 weeks, "
"or never (which is the default setting)."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le modhnóir am éaga teachtaireachta a chumrú faoi na ``Socruithe "
"Comhrá`` laistigh den rannán ``Modhnóireacht``. Nuair a shroicheann "
"teachtaireacht a ham éaga, baintear í go huathoibríoch ón gcomhrá. Is iad na"
" tréimhsí éaga atá ar fáil ná 1 uair an chloig, 8 n-uaire an chloig, 1 lá, 1"
" seachtain, 4 seachtaine, nó riamh (is é sin an socrú réamhshocraithe)."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:185
msgid "Notifications and privacy"
msgstr "Fógraí agus príobháideacht"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:187
msgid "By default, Nextcloud Talk will notify you about:"
msgstr "De réir réamhshocraithe, cuirfidh Nextcloud Talk in iúl duit faoi:"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:189
msgid "New messages in private conversations;"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí nua i gcomhráite príobháideacha;"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:190
msgid "Replies to messages you sent;"
msgstr "Freagraí ar theachtaireachtaí a sheol tú;"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:191
msgid "Messages mentioning you or group/team you are member of;"
msgstr ""
"Teachtaireachtaí ina luaitear tú féin nó grúpa/foireann ina bhfuil tú i do "
"bhall de;"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:192
msgid "Started calls in conversations you are part of."
msgstr "Glaonna tosaithe i gcomhráite ina bhfuil tú páirteach."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:194
msgid ""
"You can change this behavior in the conversation settings. Additionally, you"
" can configure:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an t-iompar seo a athrú sna socruithe comhrá. Ina theannta "
"sin, is féidir leat a chumrú:"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:196
msgid ""
"**Important conversations**: you will be always notificed about new "
"messages, even if you are in \"Do Not Disturb\" mode;"
msgstr ""
"**Comhráite tábhachtacha**: cuirfear ar an eolas thú i gcónaí faoi "
"theachtaireachtaí nua, fiú má tá tú i mód \"Ná Cuir isteach\";"

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:197
msgid ""
"**Sensitive conversations**: content of messages will not be shown in the "
"conversation list and obscured from notifications."
msgstr ""
"**Comhráite íogaire**: ní thaispeánfar ábhar teachtaireachtaí sa liosta "
"comhráite agus ní bheidh sé le feiceáil i bhfógraí."

#: ../../talk/conversations.rst:202
msgid ""
"To have more control over your privacy, you can also configure the "
"visibility of your typing and read indicators in ``Talk settings``:"
msgstr ""
"Chun níos mó smachta a bheith agat ar do phríobháideacht, is féidir leat "
"infheictheacht do tháscairí clóscríbhneoireachta agus léitheoireachta a "
"chumrú i ``Socruithe Comhrá`` freisin:"
